race.comment: BLUE ART (8) was in the money last time at this track (25.71) in a Free For All, finishing a 6 length third. Has already won four times from this draw. Makes strong appeal on best. CASH HANDY (1) ran an outstanding 19.67 when winning over 366m at Capalaba last start. Expecting another bold showing. RICOCHET RIPPLE (4) unwanted in betting but showed good early dash and led until late, finishing third and beaten 2 lengths (25.53) at this track in a Grade 5 over 457m. Expected to be in the finish again. DAINTREE GODDESS (7) can sneak into the finish.
